name: s_m_OSC_VBEZ_AccountTeamExtract
description: Session pushed from PC to ICS : s_m_OSC_VBEZ_AccountTeamExtract

parameters.name: $SQ_T_OSC_ORG$
parameters.label: SQ_T_OSC_ORG
parameters.customQuery:
SELECT org.sapidinvivo as accountid, org.countrycode as countrycode, res.username as gid, res.positiontype as positiontype, 'InVitro' as businessarea, 'Primary In Vitro (DX) Rep' as description, org.sapaccountgroup as sapaccountgroup, org.lastupdateddate_c as lastupdateddate_c
FROM osc.t_osc_org org, osc.t_osc_resource res
WHERE org.primaryinvitrorepid = res.resourceprofileid AND org.lastupdateddate_c >= to_date('$$PROCESS_DATE','MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') - 1 AND blockingstatus in ('Verified and Active','Blocked')
UNION ALL
